      • removeCar

        public Car removeCar(boolean first,
                     storage.Movable movable)
        Removes the car specified by the first parameter. If the first parameter is true, then the first car in gets removed first, and if the first parameter is false, the last car in gets removed first. The removed car is set to the position of the carrier + 1 on the y axis. If there are no cars on the trailer null is returned.
        Parameters:
        first - Specifies whether the first or last car in gets removed first
        movable - The movable object of the carrier.
        Returns:
        the removed car.
